Full Job Description:

Boutique law firm located in lower New York City seeks a full time Receptionist/Legal Administrative Assistant to join our firm. The ideal candidate would have superior organizational skills, the ability to handle a high volume and fast-paced environment, attention to detail and initiative to ensure all tasks are completed in a timely manner. Strong knowledge of Outlook, Microsoft word & Excel is required. Landlord & Tenant law experience is a plus but not required.

Description:

* Have excellent typing and word processing skills;
* Perform secretarial and clerical duties;
